This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and dependency parsing. The use of multilingual word clusters and embeddings, token-level language information, and language-specific features also suggests that it may belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper may also belong to the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves the use of neural networks for parsing.
